Description:
This domain contains data on three food value measures, namely: (1) Food At Home (FAH); (2) Food and Tobacco at Home (FTAH); 
(3) Food and Accommodation Away From Home (FAAFH), disaggregated by four primary factors (Operating Surplus, Labor, Taxes, Imports) 
and by five food value chain industries (Agriculture, Forestry and Fishing; Manufacture of food, beverages and tobacco products; 
Transportation and storage; Wholesale and retail trade; Accommodation and food service activities). The three food value measures differ
 for the bundle of goods and services they account for
